######## POSTGRESQL — MX Linux #######

Commands used:
$ sudo apt-get update
$sudo apt-get install postgresql postgresql-contrib
$ sudo -i -u postgres

$ postgres          
OR
$ sudo -u postgres psql

$ sudo -u postgres createuser –interactive
$ sudo -u postgres createdb dbname

######### INSTALL POSTGIS #################
sudo apt-get install postgresql-13-postgis-3
